{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1034971bda","title":"天津大学右派言论","origin":"《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"417a40a4b1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"1034971bda"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4dacdf1ae4","name":"杨学澹"},{"id":"c8c474caaa","name":"天津大学"},{"id":"caca0997a3","name":"王原强"},{"id":"e4774e851b","name":"卢绳"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"eee6fc5bd0","type":"title","text":"天津大学右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1034971bda"},{"id":"00a6a25c12","type":"authors","text":"天津大学卢绳杨学澹王原强","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1034971bda"},{"id":"66667d4b64","type":"paragraph","text":"“工农干部不懂业务，不学无术，虽然过去有血汗功劳，但是发个奖章给点奖金让他们回农村生产就行了，工农干部不讲理，脱产干部增加人民内部矛盾。”（天津大学  卢绳）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1034971bda"},{"id":"dcafc6bcd8","type":"paragraph","text":"“可以试行职业自由选择，这样做边区是不是没人去，不会的，党团员可以带头，还有的人为了搞自己的专业而愿意去边区。如果不想干的工作非要别人干，是绝对安不下心去的。”（天津大学  杨学澹）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1034971bda"},{"id":"2b44535209","type":"paragraph","text":"“黄绍竑解放前是一热血青年，血债不可避免，民革都有，他们的历史是不能翻的。”（天津大学  王原强）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1034971bda"}],"page":{"id":"e92600d4bf","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1034971bda","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}